██╔════╝██╔══██╗██╔══██╗██║     ██╔═══██╗██╔════╝
██║     ███████║██████╔╝██║     ██║   ██║███████╗
██║     ██╔══██║██╔══██╗██║     ██║   ██║╚════██║
╚██████╗██║  ██║██║  ██║███████╗╚██████╔╝███████║
 ╚═════╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚═╝  ╚═╝╚══════╝ ╚═════╝ ╚══════╝
                                                 
EOF
echo $(uname -a)
/dumb-init /bin/sh
/carl-exit
